.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json
.obsidian/cache

# OS noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Obsidian artifacts: 0-byte stray files materialized from unresolved [[links]].
# No git pattern catches these reliably (filenames vary) — lint-brain.ps1 flags them
# under "ROOT STRAY .md FILES"; delete by hand after a lint pass.

# NOTE on project instances:
# A project's own .brain/ is committed WITH that project's repo, not here.
# This engine repo only tracks the template, scripts, schema, and the bundled example.
